.9999999976089384, \"rank\": 2.3910678160631545e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Davis native\", \"from\": 229, \"to\": 245}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic podium\", \"from\": 262, \"to\": 280}, {\"ngram\": \"the bronze medal\", \"from\": 303, \"to\": 319}, {\"ngram\": \"a nail-biting final event\", \"from\": 323, \"to\": 348}, {\"ngram\": \"first place\", \"from\": 365, \"to\": 376}, {\"ngram\": \"the last moments\", \"from\": 383, \"to\": 399}, {\"ngram\": \"competition\", \"from\": 403, \"to\": 414}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It marks his first Olympic win after he left the 2020 Tokyo Games empty-handed.\", \"from\": 416, \"to\": 495, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his first Olympic win\", \"from\": 425, \"to\": 446}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2020 Tokyo Games\", \"from\": 461, \"to\": 481}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Huston is a six-time world champion and 13-time X Games gold medalist.\", \"from\": 497, \"to\": 567, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Huston\", \"from\": 497, \"to\": 503}, {\"ngram\": \"a six-time world champion\", \"from\": 507, \"to\": 532}, {\"ngram\": \"13-time X Games gold medalist\", \"from\": 537, \"to\": 566}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Machado says thecity is planning to builda new skate park from scratch at The Community Park along F Street and W. Covell Boulevard and they are thrilled to have Huston's help.\", \"from\": 569, \"to\": 745, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 569, \"end\": 576, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Antonio_Machado\", \"score\": 0.6085536034450708, \"rank\": 0.5365170104378124, \"text\": \"Machado\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Antonio_Machado\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Antonio_Machado\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"thecity\", \"from\": 582, \"to\": 589}, {\"ngram\": \"new skate park\", \"from\": 612, \"to\": 626}, {\"ngram\": \"scratch\", \"from\": 632, \"to\": 639}, {\"ngram\": \"The Community Park\", \"from\": 643, \"to\": 661}, {\"ngram\": \"F Street\", \"from\": 668, \"to\": 676}, {\"ngram\": \"W. Covell Boulevard\", \"from\": 681, \"to\": 700}, {\"ngram\": \"Huston's help\", \"from\": 731, \"to\": 744}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He's expressed a desire to come back and skate it before we demolish it and expressed a desire to actually contribute to the design in some way,\\\" said Deanne Machado, Parks Director for the City of Davis.\", \"from\": 747, \"to\": 952, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 906, \"end\": 913, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Antonio_Machado\", \"score\": 0.6085536034450708, \"rank\": 0.5365170104378124, \"text\": \"Machado\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Antonio_Machado\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Antonio_Machado\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a desire\", \"from\": 763, \"to\": 771}, {\"ngram\": \"a desire\", \"from\": 834, \"to\": 842}, {\"ngram\": \"the design\", \"from\": 869, \"to\": 879}, {\"ngram\": \"some way\", \"from\": 883, \"to\": 891}, {\"ngram\": \"Parks Director\", \"from\": 915, \"to\": 929}, {\"ngram\": \"the City\", \"from\": 934, \"to\": 942}, {\"ngram\": \"Davis\", \"from\": 946, \"to\": 951}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They also want the new park to reflect what the locals want to see.\", \"from\": 954, \"to\": 1021, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the new park\", \"from\": 969, \"to\": 981}, {\"ngram\": \"the locals\", \"from\": 998, \"to\": 1008}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are really relying on feedback from our local community of skateboarders,\\\" said Machado, adding they have already started putting out surveys.\", \"from\": 1023, \"to\": 1169, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1107, \"end\": 1114, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Antonio_Machado\", \"score\": 0.6085536034450708, \"rank\": 0.5365170104378124, \"text\": \"Machado\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Antonio_Machado\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Antonio_Machado\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"feedback\", \"from\": 1049, \"to\": 1057}, {\"ngram\": \"our local community\", \"from\": 1063, \"to\": 1082}, {\"ngram\": \"skateboarders\", \"from\": 1086, \"to\": 1099}, {\"ngram\": \"surveys\", \"from\": 1161, \"to\": 1168}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Jack White, skateboarder and co-founder of the Davis Skate Park Association, said he can not wait for the new park.\", \"from\": 1171, \"to\": 1286, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1171, \"end\": 1181, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_White\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0709783814867452e-26, \"text\": \"Jack White\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_White\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_White\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"co\", \"from\": 1200, \"to\": 1202}, {\"ngram\": \"founder\", \"from\": 1203, \"to\": 1210}, {\"ngram\": \"the Davis Skate Park Association\", \"from\": 1214, \"to\": 1246}, {\"ngram\": \"the new park\", \"from\": 1273, \"to\": 1285}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"After skating this park for so long, sometimes it can get a little boring and it's hard to progress,\\\" White said.\", \"from\": 1288, \"to\": 1402, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1391, \"end\": 1396, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/White_people\", \"score\": 0.999844279439325, \"rank\": 0.00011696312827079124, \"text\": \"White\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/White_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/White_people\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this park\", \"from\": 1303, \"to\": 1312}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There could be stair sets and something that represents something like the street.\", \"from\": 1403, \"to\": 1486, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"stair sets\", \"from\": 1419, \"to\": 1429}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 1434, \"to\": 1443}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 1460, \"to\": 1469}, {\"ngram\": \"the street\", \"from\": 1475, \"to\": 1485}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There could be giant pools and big bowls.\\\"\", \"from\": 1487, \"to\": 1529, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"giant pools\", \"from\": 1502, \"to\": 1513}, {\"ngram\": \"big bowls\", \"from\": 1518, \"to\": 1527}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Huston's stardom started with humble beginnings at this Davis skate park.\", \"from\": 1531, \"to\": 1604, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Huston's stardom\", \"from\": 1531, \"to\": 1547}, {\"ngram\": \"humble beginnings\", \"from\": 1561, \"to\": 1578}, {\"ngram\": \"this Davis skate park\", \"from\": 1582, \"to\": 1603}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There is lots of lore and history about Nyjah skating Davis and just being so good from an early age,\\\" White said.\", \"from\": 1606, \"to\": 1721, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1710, \"end\": 1715, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/White_people\", \"score\": 0.999844279439325, \"rank\": 0.00011696312827079124, \"text\": \"White\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/White_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/White_people\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"lots\", \"from\": 1616, \"to\": 1620}, {\"ngram\": \"lore\", \"from\": 1624, \"to\": 1628}, {\"ngram\": \"history\", \"from\": 1633, \"to\": 1640}, {\"ngram\": \"Nyjah\", \"from\": 1647, \"to\": 1652}, {\"ngram\": \"Davis\", \"from\": 1661, \"to\": 1666}, {\"ngram\": \"an early age\", \"from\": 1695, \"to\": 1707}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Huston's road to becoming one of the best in his sport was not easy.\", \"from\": 1723, \"to\": 1791, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Huston's road\", \"from\": 1723, \"to\": 1736}, {\"ngram\": \"his sport\", \"from\": 1768, \"to\": 1777}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His family was navigating divorce, custody battles and financial trouble when his mother enrolled him in the first-ever Street League Skateboarding event in Arizona.\", \"from\": 1793, \"to\": 1958, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1913, \"end\": 1940, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Street_League_Skateboarding\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Street League Skateboarding\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Street_League_Skateboarding\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Street_League_Skateboarding\"}, {\"begin\": 1950, \"end\": 1957, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arizona\", \"score\": 0.9979960591932068, \"rank\": 0.0015382308209031788, \"text\": \"Arizona\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arizona\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arizona\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"His family\", \"from\": 1793, \"to\": 1803}, {\"ngram\": \"divorce\", \"from\": 1819, \"to\": 1826}, {\"ngram\": \"custody battles\", \"from\": 1828, \"to\": 1843}, {\"ngram\": \"financial trouble\", \"from\": 1848, \"to\": 1865}, {\"ngram\": \"his mother\", \"from\": 1871, \"to\": 1881}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She was left with less than $100 to her name.\", \"from\": 1959, \"to\": 2004, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her name\", \"from\": 1995, \"to\": 2003}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"When we needed it the most, I made it happen,\\\" Huston said in an interview with CBS News.\", \"from\": 2006, \"to\": 2096, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2087, \"end\": 2095, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CBS_News\", \"score\": 0.9835488123184387, \"rank\": 0.016726356095075945, \"text\": \"CBS News\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CBS_News\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CBS_News\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Huston\", \"from\": 2054, \"to\": 2060}, {\"ngram\": \"an interview\", \"from\": 2069, \"to\": 2081}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Huston won big, bringing home $150,000 and financial stability to his family at just 15 years old.\", \"from\": 2098, \"to\": 2196, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Huston\", \"from\": 2098, \"to\": 2104}, {\"ngram\": \"$150,000 and financial stability\", \"from\": 2128, \"to\": 2160}, {\"ngram\": \"his family\", \"from\": 2164, \"to\": 2174}]}, {\"sentence\": \"From there, the sky was the limit.\", \"from\": 2197, \"to\": 2231, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the sky\", \"from\": 2209, \"to\": 2216}, {\"ngram\": \"the limit\", \"from\": 2221, \"to\": 2230}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think the fact I was able to get through those rough moments as a kid and still come out with that much love for it, it's the perfect example of how fun skateboarding is, and it's really just an addiction.\", \"from\": 2233, \"to\": 2441, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the fact\", \"from\": 2242, \"to\": 2250}, {\"ngram\": \"those rough moments\", \"from\": 2277, \"to\": 2296}, {\"ngram\": \"a kid\", \"from\": 2300, \"to\": 2305}, {\"ngram\": \"that much love\", \"from\": 2330, \"to\": 2344}, {\"ngram\": \"the perfect example\", \"from\": 2358, \"to\": 2377}, {\"ngram\": \"how fun\", \"from\": 2381, \"to\": 2388}, {\"ngram\": \"just an addiction\", \"from\": 2423, \"to\": 2440}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There is nothing else like it,\\\" said Huston.\", \"from\": 2442, \"to\": 2486, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"nothing\", \"from\": 2451, \"to\": 2458}, {\"ngram\": \"Huston\", \"from\": 2479, \"to\": 2485}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now, his hometown of Davis is building on his journey.\", \"from\": 2488, \"to\": 2542, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his hometown\", \"from\": 2493, \"to\": 2505}, {\"ngram\": \"Davis\", \"from\": 2509, \"to\": 2514}, {\"ngram\": \"his journey\", \"from\": 2530, \"to\": 2541}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Nyjah's story is inspiring.\", \"from\": 2544, \"to\": 2572, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Nyjah's story\", \"from\": 2545, \"to\": 2558}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He did grow up in this skate park.If he can achieve that level of greatness having gotten his start here in this skatepark, which can be definitely improved, how much more wonderful would it be for us to improve it and make it even better?\", \"from\": 2573, \"to\": 2812, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this skate park\", \"from\": 2591, \"to\": 2606}, {\"ngram\": \"that level\", \"from\": 2625, \"to\": 2635}, {\"ngram\": \"greatness\", \"from\": 2639, \"to\": 2648}, {\"ngram\": \"his start\", \"from\": 2663, \"to\": 2672}, {\"ngram\": \"this skatepark\", \"from\": 2681, \"to\": 2695}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 2771, \"to\": 2773}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That whole new generation of young people can come in and dream big just like Nyjah,\\\" said Machado.\", \"from\": 2813, \"to\": 2912, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2904, \"end\": 2911, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Antonio_Machado\", \"score\": 0.6085536034450708, \"rank\": 0.5365170104378124, \"text\": \"Machado\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Antonio_Machado\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Antonio_Machado\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"That whole new generation\", \"from\": 2813, \"to\": 2838}, {\"ngram\": \"young people\", \"from\": 2842, \"to\": 2854}, {\"ngram\": \"Nyjah\", \"from\": 2891, \"to\": 2896}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Davis' city council has already approved the renovation project which will be funded with local American Rescue Plan dollars.\", \"from\": 2914, \"to\": 3039, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3010, \"end\": 3030, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_Rescue_Plan_Act_of_2021\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"American Rescue Plan\", \"types\":